Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:48.70,SongJap,,0,0,0,,時間が止まる 光と空の森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:48.70,SongChn,,0,0,0,,光线和天空的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:54.04,SongChn,,0,0,0,,风儿传递着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:21:00.05,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K90}ka{\K80}ze {\K60}ga {\K50}ha{\K50}ko{\K50}bu  {\K120}{\K65}ka{\K65}su{\K65}ka {\K60}na {\K60}se{\K40}se{\K40}ra{\K60}gi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:21:00.05,SongJap,,0,0,0,,風が運ぶ かすかなせせらぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:21:00.05,SongChn,,0,0,0,,细细的溪流声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:11.47,SongChn,,0,0,0,,你看闪闪发光的湖面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:11.47,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K85}ho{\K85}ra  {\K60}{\K50}ma{\K40}bu{\K40}shi{\K40}ku {\K80}{\K80}hi{\K75}ka{\K110}ru {\K85}mi{\K40}zuu{\K65}mi {\K80}wa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:11.47,SongJap,,0,0,0,,ほら まぶしく光る湖は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:25.91,SongChn,,0,0,0,,成为镜子映出那天失去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:18.67,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K120}ano {\K60}hi {\K70}ni {\K60}{\K50}na{\K40}ku{\K40}shi{\K60}ta {\K60}mo{\K50}no {\K60}wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:18.67,SongJap,,0,0,0,,あの日に失くしたものを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:25.91,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K60}utsu{\K60}shi{\K60}da{\K60}su {\K50}{\K40}ka{\K40}ga{\K60}mi {\K200}ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:25.91,SongJap,,0,0,0,,映し出す鏡に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:35.89,SongChn,,0,0,0,,幸福一定和悲哀很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:35.89,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K80}kit{\K60}to {\K30}shi{\K30}a{\K20}wa{\K20}se {\K200}wa {\K80}{\K60}ka{\K50}na{\K50}shi{\K50}mi {\K30}ni {\K30}ni{\K30}tei{\K90}ru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:35.89,SongJap,,0,0,0,,きっと幸せは 哀しみに似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:43.93,SongChn,,0,0,0,,闭上心灵的瞳眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:54.04,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K60}ko{\K60}ko{\K60}ro {\K100}no {\K70}hi{\K50}to{\K50}mi {\K60}to{\K40}ji{\K70}te  {\K60}{\K70}so{\K70}tto {\K80}{\K70}so{\K70}ra {\K110}wo {\K110}da{\K220}ku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:54.04,SongJap,,0,0,0,,心の瞳閉じて そっと空を抱く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:54.04,SongChn,,0,0,0,,轻轻地拥抱天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,下一回也一定要看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最优先事项喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂，别人说跟你在一起\N我一定会不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你才停滞的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你要对自己更有自信一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在你身边，很幸福喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你的停滞才是我的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快点醒过来，小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们两人一起加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,星空的邂逅下一回\N“老师不要哭”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要看喔\N这是最优先事项喔
